DP.Name: Load_Status_Code
DP.CodedSet: 0=Waiting for Data Load; 1=Loading File; 2=File Loaded; 3=CRC Complete

DP.Name: I_or_O_Status_Code
DP.CodedSet: 0=No Failure; 2=Bad Status; 3=No Data Loader Response; 4=Bad Data Loader Response

DP.Name: HF_Fuel_Inhibition
DP.ZeroState: 0=HF Tx Not Inhibited Due to Fueling

DP.Name: Fuel_Operations_Status
DP.OneState: 1=Fuel operation in progress, All TX inhibited
DP.ZeroState: 0=No fuel operation in progress, All TX uninhibited except for Datalink on ground unless verridden

DP.Name: HFDL_Tx_Inhibit_Override
DP.OneState: 1 = HFDL Tx Inhibit is not override

DP.Name: HFDR_2_Voice_Or_data
DP.OneState: 1 = Voice mode or Analog non-HFDL Data

DP.Name: First_Word_Indication
DP.OneState: 1=Set to 1 for the first label 354 of the block
DP.ZeroState: 0=Set to 0 for other 354 labels of the block
